<br>
6 wizards target a mob, and go &quot;Boom&quot; with SoS.  22 k average damage (with foci and crits).  2 volley's = 44 k damage.<br>
<br>
You can probably take down a summoning 18 k hp mob before it kills a group member with good syncronization.<br>
<br>
6 mages /pet attack a mob, and then go &quot;boom&quot; with FoT.  15 k damage from 300 range, with 2nd bolt INC before first one arrives.  Stun pets slow the mob's charge down and do some damage.  3 volley's = 45 k damage + incidental pet damage.<br>
<br>
Most servers probably don't have 6 LFG mages or wizards at the same time however, but the idea is sorta neat.<br>
